bodyEn:
1. Despite adequate FASTag balance on {TAG_ID} (vehicle {VEHICLE_NO}) with {BANK_NAME}, plaza {PLAZA_NAME} deducted a 'negative-balance penalty' of Rs. {AMOUNT} on {TXN_DATE} (UTR {UTR}). Negative balance should not arise on an issuer wallet — reverse the penalty.

Attachments: Tag statement, plaza receipt, ANPR screenshot (if available).

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
